== Event Description ==
[[File:Crosswave Event Banner EN.png|500px]]

*In this event, Suruga will be the boss and all the Commanders in the Server will need to work together to defeat Suruga.
**Participating in the event '''will cost oil''' depending on fleet used.
*In EX map, when the timer runs out, or if your fleet is defeated, contribution value will be given according to the total damage done.
*The battle in EX map has a total time limit of 60 seconds. The higher the damage you deal, the better the rewards are and contributions you will get. If you withdraw from battle, you will not receive any reward.
*The other maps will have a time limit of 3 minutes, and the boss must be defeated to obtain contribution points.
*Each server's progression will be calculated separately. When the Gauge reaches 0%, the event will be successfully completed.

== Event Stage ==
* The event stage has 4 difficulties: Easy, Normal, Hard, and EX. The Contribution Point [[File:SurugaPt.png|25px]] gain will increase along with the difficulties. To access the EX stage you will need a Special Pass [[File:SurugaTicket.png|30px]] and the point gain will be based on how much damage you have done (Note: Practice mode is available for EX).
** Levels for the four difficulties:
*** Easy: Lvl 30 (30 [[File:SurugaPt.png|25px]])
*** Normal: Lvl 60 (70 [[File:SurugaPt.png|25px]])
*** Hard: Lvl 100 (120 [[File:SurugaPt.png|25px]])
*** EX: Lvl 125 ([[File:SurugaPt.png|25px]] rewarded will vary depending on damage dealt to the boss for 60 seconds)
* Your first 15 battles for each day on each of the Easy, Normal and Hard difficulties will give you better clear rewards. If you have used up all 15 sorties, you can use a Special pass [[File:SurugaTicket.png|30px]] to keep getting better clear rewards. 
**You can still play the event maps (except for EX) after using up the daily sorties, even with zero Special passes. The amount of contribution points will stay the same.
* Submarines and Meowfficers can be used. Summoning submarines will cost fuel.
